0.1.2
-----
Updated zvtm-fits to use the new zvtm coordinate system (starting
with zvtm 0.11.0). The new system uses double precision floating point coordinates.
zvtm-fits now depends on zvtm 0.11.0

0.1.1
-----
Added a zscale-like transform (linear scaling; the 'transform' simply
selects appropriate parameters)
Added default choices for color filters (ColorFilter enum).

0.1.0
-----
First tag. Added color filters.


